title: Gang Starr - Full Clip: A Decade of Gang Starr
description: Full Clip: A Decade of Gang Starr is a compilation album, featuring 32 songs released by Hip Hop duo Gang Starr between 1989 and 1999, plus a brief 'intro' track. It was released by Virgin Records.
